export.description:
Tomb of Horrors (Under Constructon): Acererak built a number of dungeons and tombs, including the Tomb of Horrors.

The tomb wasn't always a great monument to Acererak's infamy, for all stories have a beginning. While under construction, the Tomb of Horrors was a different kind of place.
